description: These kaomojis are doing that thing one does when they’ve achieved success by raising a fist upwards and then pulling it back down in celebration. I swear they are saying a silent, “yes!” This is an awesome celebrating emoticon to use for any grand success. It could be your own accomplishment, that of a friend’s, or even your favourite sports team.
